---- Assignment 4: Maximum Profit ----
### Objective
Practice how to write a Python program that includes basic components and basic algorithms.
### Description
You are given an array prices where prices[i] represents the price of a stock on the i th day.

Your task is to determine the maximum profit that can be obtained by selecting a single day to buy one stock and a different day in the future to sell that stock.

You may not sell a stock before you buy it. If no profit can be made, return 0.


- Input Formats
A single line containing space-separated integers representing the stock prices over days.

- Output Formats
A single integer representing the maximum profit that can be achieved.
If no profit is possible, return 0.